                            空終止字串
                        </div>
                    

                    

                    



                    <div id="page-content">
                        

<div style="text-align: center;">
<p><sub><strong>&#171;</strong> <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/aiad-homescreen">HUB</a> | <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/alert-lockdown-initiated">第一部份</a> | <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/command-query-separation">第二部份</a> | <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/superencipherment">第三部份</a> | <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/clock-multiplier">第四部份</a> | <span style="color: blue">第五部份: 空終止字串</span> <strong>&#187;</strong></sub></p>
</div>
<hr />



<p><br />
<br /></p>
<div style="float:left; text-align: left; margin: 0 0 10px 10px; width: 240px;">
<div style="text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px; color: #fff0f0; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #C0504D; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius: 8px; -moz-border-radius: 8px; border-radius: 8px;">
<p>所以這是你的官方意見嗎？</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/null-terminating-string/bozkurt2.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="bozkurt2.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div style="float:right; text-align: right; margin: 0 0 10px 10px; width: 240px;">
<div style="text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px; color: #fff0f0; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #7F7F7F; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius: 8px; -moz-border-radius: 8px; border-radius: 8px;">
<p>直到目前為止，是的。雖然我們不排除是有人蓄意破壞&#8230;&#8230;當然，有待調查。</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/null-terminating-string/lurk2.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="lurk2.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div style="float:left; text-align: left; margin: 0 0 10px 10px; width: 240px;">
<div style="text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px; color: #fff0f0; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #C0504D; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius: 8px; -moz-border-radius: 8px; border-radius: 8px;">
<p>那好吧。我會這樣告訴主管的。他認為伺服器並不會毫無來由地就這樣燒起來。坦白說，我傾向於同意他的看法。</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/null-terminating-string/bozkurt2.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="bozkurt2.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div style="float:right; text-align: right; margin: 0 0 10px 10px; width: 240px;">
<div style="text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px; color: #fff0f0; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #7F7F7F; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius: 8px; -moz-border-radius: 8px; border-radius: 8px;">
<p>呵呵。問題是除了鎖閉以外，並沒什麼東西跑掉或跑進來。即使有事件記錄也和其他檔案一起被毀掉了。</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/null-terminating-string/lurk2.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="lurk2.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div style="float:left; text-align: left; margin: 0 0 10px 10px; width: 240px;">
<div style="text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px; color: #fff0f0; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #C0504D; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius: 8px; -moz-border-radius: 8px; border-radius: 8px;">
<p>所以我們永遠不知道事情是怎樣搞出來的？</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/null-terminating-string/bozkurt2.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="bozkurt2.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div style="float:right; text-align: right; margin: 0 0 10px 10px; width: 240px;">
<div style="text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px; color: #fff0f0; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #7F7F7F; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius: 8px; -moz-border-radius: 8px; border-radius: 8px;">
<p>你大可再翻一翻看看有沒有東西還沒熔成渣的。</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/null-terminating-string/lurk2.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="lurk2.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div style="float:left; text-align: left; margin: 0 0 10px 10px; width: 240px;">
<div style="text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px; color: #fff0f0; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #C0504D; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius: 8px; -moz-border-radius: 8px; border-radius: 8px;">
<p>免了。我想最值得寬慰的是事件只發生在伺服器室裡。全都能透過站外備份還原回來。</p>
<p>那Glacon怎了？</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/null-terminating-string/bozkurt2.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="bozkurt2.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div style="float:right; text-align: right; margin: 0 0 10px 10px; width: 240px;">
<div style="text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px; color: #fff0f0; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #7F7F7F; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius: 8px; -moz-border-radius: 8px; border-radius: 8px;">
<p>總之他是被廢除了。</p>
<p>Alexandra目前在19的伺服為17分配空間。設置臨時符號鏈接什麼的。會做到硬件都更換完為止。</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/null-terminating-string/lurk2.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="lurk2.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div style="float:left; text-align: left; margin: 0 0 10px 10px; width: 240px;">
<div style="text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px; color: #fff0f0; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #C0504D; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius: 8px; -moz-border-radius: 8px; border-radius: 8px;">
<p>很好。AIAD目前看起來不錯，能幫17快速回到正軌上。如果最近的一些預算請求能獲得通過的話我也不會感到驚訝的。</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/null-terminating-string/bozkurt2.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="bozkurt2.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div style="float:right; text-align: right; margin: 0 0 10px 10px; width: 240px;">
<div style="text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px; color: #fff0f0; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #7F7F7F; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius: 8px; -moz-border-radius: 8px; border-radius: 8px;">
<p>對阿。然後這些都會撥到你的部門的第五世代研發項目上呢。</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/null-terminating-string/lurk2.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="lurk2.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div style="float:left; text-align: left; margin: 0 0 10px 10px; width: 240px;">
<div style="text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px; color: #fff0f0; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #C0504D; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius: 8px; -moz-border-radius: 8px; border-radius: 8px;">
<p>希望出來的結果會比第三世代好，至少如此吧！</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/null-terminating-string/bozkurt2.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="bozkurt2.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div style="float:right; text-align: right; margin: 0 0 10px 10px; width: 240px;">
<div style="text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px; color: #fff0f0; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #7F7F7F; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius: 8px; -moz-border-radius: 8px; border-radius: 8px;">
<p><em>說好不提</em>第三世代的。<em>永遠別提。</em></p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/null-terminating-string/lurk2.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="lurk2.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div style="float:left; text-align: left; margin: 0 0 10px 10px; width: 240px;">
<div style="text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px; color: #fff0f0; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #C0504D; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius: 8px; -moz-border-radius: 8px; border-radius: 8px;">
<p>對對，不好意思。</p>
<p>話說，Alexandra的行為在此之後變得怎樣呢？</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/null-terminating-string/bozkurt2.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="bozkurt2.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div style="float:right; text-align: right; margin: 0 0 10px 10px; width: 240px;">
<div style="text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px; color: #fff0f0; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #7F7F7F; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius: 8px; -moz-border-radius: 8px; border-radius: 8px;">
<p>遠比我所知的好。她一直都在忙著呢。</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/null-terminating-string/lurk2.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="lurk2.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<br />
<br />
<br />
<div style="clear:both; height: 0px; font-size: 1px"></div>
